headline: News Corp to Report Fiscal 2026 First Quarter Earnings
summary: NEW YORK, October 23, 2025--News Corp will release its first quarter Fiscal 2026 results on Thursday, November 6, 2025. News Corp Chief Executive Robert Thomson and Chief Financial Officer Lavanya Chandrashekar will discuss the results via a live audio webcast at 5:00 p.m. EST (Sydney: November 7, at 9:00 a.m. AEDT).

headline: The Wall Street Journal Announces Launch of WSJ Invest Live
summary: NEW YORK, October 23, 2025--The Wall Street Journal announced today the launch of WSJ Invest Live, a first-of-its-kind, high-impact, editorially led event dedicated to the forces shaping global finance, hosted in West Palm Beach, Florida, February 2-3, 2026.
